msgid ""
"I'm still not sure of your strength. Your victory could be an accident. I "
"will fight you every day until I am convinced that you are worthy to receive "
"my wings."
msgstr "我仍然不確定你的實力，你的勝利可能只是偶然。我會每天和你戰鬥，直到我相信你配得上我的翅膀。"

